HEADWORD: Good-tempered
<hw>Good`-tem"pered</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having a good
temper; not easily vexed or irritated. See
<er>Good-natured</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> equable, even-tempered, placid.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>good-time</ent>⟦br⟧
